    "The tool assessment had two components: the misuse-relevant capability assessment and an assessment of maturity and availability.",
    "We describe three components of the Global Risk Index briefly below, with more details on these and others available in Appendix A.",
    "Given the speed of development of AI tools in the life sciences, this assessment aimed to highlight tools with uncertain but potentially rapid development trajectories.",
